            "body": "Thanks -- this makes a lot more sense now.\n\n> Although looking at Numpy's definition of ndarray, they include check_size ignore so if you're seeing it you've got an old/odd version of something\n\nIt's being triggered, I think, by the netCDF4 lib, not numpy:\n\nhttps://github.com/Unidata/netcdf4-python\n\nBut I don't see where ...., so maybe not?\n\n\n",
