            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "There are cases in which that library generates a Limited API wheel:\nhttps://github.com/Unidata/netcdf4-python/blob/25c1684eae440d733f1ea05ffdeb386b2a9ae559/setup.py#L12-L26\n\nThe unrealistic \"16 bytes\" (a single pointer?) size in the warning suggests to me that your installation might be mixing Limited API modules with non-LAPI modules where both disagree about the size. (Although I think we have at least some guards for this case.)",
